----

Use this template to show a highlighted block of text for very important messages, such as to warn the user of an incompatibility or obsolete function. Use it rarely!

Example:

 <nowiki>
{{VeryImportantMessage|Warning: this is an important message}}</nowiki>

Result:

{{VeryImportantMessage|Warning: this is an important message}}

See also:

* [[Template:Message]] for not so important messages.

